This Snapshot Released On Thursday April 2 2026
Added Report Issue Link Here https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux/issues

For Existing Triaxis Users

Open Terminal Then sudo nano /etc/os-release
Then Change BUG_REPORT_URL="https://gitlab.archlinux.org/groups/archlinux/-/issues" To BUG_REPORT_URL="https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux/issues"
